<span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(65, 152, 0);"><strong>Facilities at startpoint:</strong></span></strong><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">Cafe, Car Park, Toilets</span></span></span></div>
